    Because of the method findResidueInternal in ThisOrTargetAnnotationPointcut.class set the var  to shadow.getTargetVar() instead of shadow.getTargetAnnotationVar, the method visit(HasAnnotation hasAnn) of the SubtypeSensitiveVarTypeTestVisitor class in RuntimeTestWalker.class in the spring source code has an error.
